GET {{baseUrl}}/cat

### Test 2: POST - Add a new cat (Whiskers)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cat_name": "Whiskers",
  "weight": 9,
  "owner": 3609,
  "filename": "whiskers_pic_001",
  "birthdate": "2022-05-15"
}

### Test 3: GET all cats again (should now show 3 cats including Whiskers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cat

